<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA512_04_IH_0006_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema512_04.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema512_04_ih_0006">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="6" class="is_star" lang="y">플라스틱을 재활용하여 만든 가방 45개와 열쇠고리 60개를 최대한 많은 사람에게 남김없이 똑같이 나누어 주려고 합니다. 가방과 열쇠고리를 최대 몇 명에게 나누어 줄 수 있는지 구해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="flex dir_col justify_start align_center gap_10">
          <div class="img_box">
            <div class="img_wrap">
              <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA512_04_IH/0006_img.png" alt="" />
              <span class="txt">
                <span class="color1" lang="y">플라스틱</span>
                <span class="color2" lang="y">재활용 제품</span>
                <span class="color3" lang="y">체험</span>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="question_box">
            (
            <div class="input_wrap ml_12 mr_12">
              <math-field data-answer-single="15"></math-field>
            </div>
            ) <span lang="y">명</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <div class="text_group mt_12">
                  <div class="row">
                    <span>3</span>
                    <span>45</span>
                    <span>60</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="row">
                    <span>5</span>
                    <span>15</span>
                    <span>20</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="row">
                    <span>3</span>
                    <span>4</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <p class="mt_12" lang="y">➔ 최대공약수: 3×5=15</p>
                <p lang="y">따라서 최대 15명에게 나누어 줄 수 있습니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
